reviews.review_text: 1981 brilliance on display Lots to love with this show, esp. the 2nd set. Languid Scarlet Fire, plenty of Bobby vocal histrionics at the end of Estimated, Heartfelt He's Gone (great Bobby/Brent harmonizing at the end). Post/drums doesn't let up either: lovely Spanish/O1 jam, Truckin' barely stays on the road, Black Peter has nice upbeat excursion at the end. Well worth the listen!
